Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:34.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:41.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胎兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:44.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉體變化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:44.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Metamorphose
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:48.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種能力  連聽都沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:08.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:10.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:21.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:24.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同學  你什麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同學  不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:37.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能下來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:42.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:43.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在那裏別出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:45.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:47.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要動手  對手就應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:50.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不追過來？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:54.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是毫無目的的失控嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:59.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像因為什麼而很痛苦的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:06.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:10.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  之前的那些患者突然失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:11.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意識已經恢復了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  剛才為止還一直在昏睡狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:15.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:16.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:22.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的患者都發生了同種癥狀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:27.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還沒恢復意識  猶如做了惡夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:31.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…發生了什麼事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:43.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪獸麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來歷不明的生物武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有能動的人都上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允許使用實彈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:51.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼好像變得越來越大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:17.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:20.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到居然會產生那種怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發表到學界上一定會得到表彰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網絡已經脫離我的控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:32.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回那些孩子們的生命和讓大家恢復都已經不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:35.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:52.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AIM擴散力場的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必是其聚合體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:55.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:59.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且就叫它「幻想猛獸」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:59.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,328)\fs18}AIM Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:03.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過幻想御手的網絡所積聚的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:03.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:06.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一萬人的AIM擴散力場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:10.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以其為媒介所產生的潛在意識的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:17.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  那就是那一萬名孩子們思想的結合體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:29.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這個城市  我本應該能實現我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為能力者的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:34.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:39.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想終究是夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎樣努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:48.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這座城市裏都會有名為才能的高牆阻擋著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只留下了悲慘的日常  被踐踏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:56.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被置若罔聞的…每一天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:03.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有入手那個了不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:08.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有即使不擇手段也要得到力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:24.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得很可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:28.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做才能阻止那個東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:31.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在問我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我即便說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:34.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也不會相…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:40.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手銬  是木山老師解開的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:48.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是一時興起而已  憑這個就信任我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:50.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:59.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救孩子們的木山老師是不可能說謊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:02.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:09.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽見了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:14.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:21.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想猛獸是幻想御手的網絡所產生的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:21.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(180,328)\fs18}AIM Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:21.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:24.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能把網絡破壞了說不定就能阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想御手的治療程序
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:31.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有嘗試一下的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:41.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙我會想辦法對付
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:45.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春就趁這個機會把它送到警備員那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:45.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:47.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:58.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  沒有根據就相信別人的人那麼多真叫人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:02.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要  別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在發什麼呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通人來這裏想幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:36.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪個傢伙嘴裏都老是叨念著什麼普通人普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:43.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  馬上逃離這…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:48.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:52.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙只要對方不攻擊就不會攻過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:57.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此也不可以撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:00.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那裏是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:02.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是核動力實驗反應爐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:06.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子在幹些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:08.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被木山作為人質的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:14.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在混亂當中沒來得及逃離嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:19.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春已經不是什麼人質也不是什麼來不及逃離的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:39.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讓人把話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:44.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  沒有損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:10:59.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然大家就來不及…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:07.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說我也是風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:07.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:09.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將佐天同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:19.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:20.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:22.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的孩子還真會亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:24.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治療程序呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完好無損
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:28.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負責掩護  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:31.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別給我東張西望的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:39.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過你的對手是我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別丟人地在那亂叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:45.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面向我攻過來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:55.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要將殺毒軟體在整個學園都市中播放
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:58.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能將幻想御手的網絡破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:58.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:01.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果戴著花飾的小姑娘那裏一切順利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:05.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能夠平息幻想猛獸的暴動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:05.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}AIM Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:21.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒完沒了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:26.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  為什麼偏偏朝著核動力設施去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是怪獸電影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:35.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是一萬名孩子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:40.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:58.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:12:59.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:03.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不惜一切方法讓我現在傳輸給你的音頻文件響徹整個學園都市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:05.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳送完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:08.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有責任由我來承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之立刻給我播放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:28.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生  患者們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:41.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裏開始決不能放它過去  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:49.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:57.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  無論受到什麼樣的攻擊它都能立即再生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:58.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那攻擊還有什麼意義…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有再生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:03.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首曲子就是治療程序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:05.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春她做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:13.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉  這下遊戲該結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:31.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是千鈞一髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:32.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…為什麼你會在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:38.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算成功破壞了網絡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:46.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那可是由AIM擴散力場產生的結合一萬人思念的結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:48.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通生物的常識是用不到它身上的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:50.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你剛才說的不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:52.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說要怎麼做才能打倒它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:58.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在它身上應該藏有一顆固定其力場的類似核的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:00.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把它破壞的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:02.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:08.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無能力者是缺陷品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:08.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(285,328)\fs18}Level 0
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:09.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要讓他們瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:11.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:12.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無能力者…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Level 0
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:15.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:19.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們每天有多麼辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能你無法理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:25.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份期待  有時也會覺得過於沉重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:30.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先退開  不然會被牽連的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:33.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  那個怪物的產生是我的責任…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:36.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你無所謂  但你的那些學生怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:39.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當他們睜開眼睛時最想看見的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是你的面容麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:45.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你別用這種做法的話  我也會幫助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別輕言放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:56.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是擔心你會被它牽連
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正可能把你捲進來的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:01.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:07.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是與我當時使用過的相同的誘電力場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:10.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以她的力量來說果然太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:18.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電擊並沒有直接擊中它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:22.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  由於受到強制誘導抵消電流的高溫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導致體表組織被逐漸擊散
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:28.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在與我交戰時  她並沒有使出全力麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:39.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:43.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經無論如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:45.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都想要成為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一名能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:48.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都沒能注意到這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是無可奈何的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:54.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:16:59.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也曾很想要努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:02.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭毫無力量的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:07.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都無法割捨這份憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  你就再努力一次試試
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:18.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在這種地方畏畏縮縮的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:22.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別對自己說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:24.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再努力一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:37.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:51.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:12.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗用爐心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及其周邊設施的檢測也完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:17.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.06,0:18:18.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:22.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再確認一次設施周圍是否有負傷者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:28.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:33.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…孩子們的事你有何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:39.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然不會輕易放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:41.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會重新開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:45.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是在監獄還是世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:49.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的腦袋還在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次我也會不擇手段
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:57.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是看不慣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屆時歡迎前來搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:07.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:09.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個記不住教訓的老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:14.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:13.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子可擔心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心都快痛得四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的頭髮都亂成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有肌膚上那數不盡的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:27.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來您是把電流一點不剩地全射出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:33.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  就讓黑子徹徹底底地來幫您把身上的每一處傷口都治癒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:34.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才從醫院接到聯絡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:43.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說幻想御手的使用者們陸續恢復意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:43.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(210,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:47.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是你的功勞哦  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:51.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  來吧  姐姐大人～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:54.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…你要幹什麼…放開我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:14.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦什麼呦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:27.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在病房讓我找了好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:30.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.32,0:20:32.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼地方感覺不舒服麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過睡了會兒罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:37.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全恢復原狀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連用不了能力這點也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:56.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:21:01.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我總是對那點小事耿耿於懷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:03.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還瞞著你去作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害初春吃了那麼多苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:08.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:17.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差點就失去比能力什麼的更加寶貴的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:22.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:25.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:28.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:36.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才醒來那麼一會兒  幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來的慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:41.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  初春  連內褲都…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:44.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這起事件算是告一段落了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:49.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:52.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:22:00.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「使用幻想御手的人們真的做錯了麼」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:22:00.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:07.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我們這些沒能察覺到他們心聲的能力者才是這起事件的真正元兇吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:11.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十有八九  在考慮這樣的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:15.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別學我啊  真讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:18.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是符合姐姐大人的溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:23.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了溫柔  還希望您能注意一下另一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:25.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.58,0:22:29.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子的心意  啾～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:31.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝你了  黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:36.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你一如既往的變態舉動  總算讓我找回狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:38.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  佐天同學總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.09,0:22:40.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.18,0:22:44.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.54,0:22:46.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學  你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:48.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:33.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊  過了一個大關才開一個什麼泳裝會是不是太小氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.11,0:23:36.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在說些什麼呢  顧客就是上帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:38.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把黑子的萬種風情給…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.42,0:23:39.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不看

